                <p class="content-body">Every AI assistant on the market today can generate confident-sounding responses that turn out to be inaccurate. This isn't a bug we can patch. It's a known limitation of the underlying technology. The risk to us is proportional to how much our teams rely on Atlas without checking its work.</p>
