                <p class="content-subhead">What we're doing about it:</p>
                <p class="content-body">We've added source links to every Atlas response so employees can verify claims with one click. Teams in Legal and Finance operate under a mandatory review policy before acting on Atlas outputs. We're tracking error rates monthly and will flag any use case where accuracy falls below our threshold.</p>
