                <h3 class="content-heading">When a user reports that Atlas gave them wrong information:</h3>
                <p class="content-body">Lead with acknowledgment. Don't minimize it. If Atlas told them their Q3 revenue was $4.2M and the real number was $3.8M, that's a real problem for them.</p>
